<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-1773] Python library should run on python 2.4</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-1773</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As of 0.9, the Python code seems to require Python &amp;gt;= 2.6 (eg using new syntax not available in 2.4). Since many people still run Thrift-based apps on RHEL5, which includes only 2.4, we should avoid this dependency.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12618629">THRIFT-1773</key>
            <summary>Python library should run on python 2.4</summary>
